subject: Basketball

Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Jordan Theodore scored a career-high 29 points to lead Seton Hall to the signature win it needed for its N.C.A.A. tournament credentials, a 73-55 victory over No. 9 Georgetown in Newark.
